downloads.name: SKAdNetwork Profile
downloads.description: This profile reduces the duration of the multiple conversion windows of SKAdNetwork postbacks. With this profile installed, the installed app has 2 minutes to update the conversion value for each postback after initial registration, and each postback will be sent within another 5 minutes after that timer expires. Effectively, you will have a 2 minute window to update each postback, instead of 0-2 days for the first, 3-7 days for the second, and 8-35 days for the third postback.

downloads.name: Advanced Video Quality Tool
downloads.description: The Advanced Video Quality Tool, or AVQT in short, is a macOS command line tool, which estimates perceptual video quality of compressed videos, that might contain video coding and scaling artifacts. The tool expects reference (source) and test (compressed) videos as inputs and outputs frame level and segment level scores of the test video on a scale of 1 to 5, where 1 indicates bad video quality and 5 indicates excellent video quality. You can also use AVQT to compute MSE (Mean Squared Error) and PSNR (Peak Signal to Noise Ratio) scores. Please see the enclosed README for more details.

downloads.name: AU Lab
downloads.description:
Apple's reference digital audio mixing application, AU Lab, can be used as a host application for Audio Unit effects, instruments, and generators.

AU Lab has a very high performance and low overhead audio engine capable of supporting multiple outputs, multichannel, and advanced routing features such as send and sidechain buses.

It also includes MIDI facilities for instruments and effects including host clock synchronization, and an inspector that features a cocoa-based generic view for Audio Units that do not provide their own custom interface. This inspector includes full support for preset management and facilities for MIDI mapping of audio unit parameters.

Designed for Audio Unit auditioning and live music applications, this is the perfect host for testing Audio Units in development.
